%20class%3D%22italic%22%3E%22YTMND%2C%20an%20acronym%20for%20You're%20The%20Man%20Now%2C%20Dog!'%2C%20is%20a%20website%20community%20that%20centers%20around%20the%20creation%20of%20YTMNDs%2C%20which%20are%20pages%20featuring%20a%20juxtaposition%20of%20a%20single%20image%2C%20optionally%20animated%20or%20tiled%2C%20along%20with%20large%20zooming%20text%20and%20a%20looping%20sound%20file.%20YTMND%20is%20also%20the%20general%20term%20used%20to%20describe%20any%20such%20site.%22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FYTMND%22%20title%3D%22Wikipedia%22%3EWikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%0A%20%3Ch2%3EThe%20history%20of%20YTMND%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%20%3Ch3%3EHow%20it%20began%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20The%20world%20was%20different%20in%202001%3B%20it%20was%20a%20simpler%20time%20and%20the%20Internet%20was%20a%20humbler%20place.%20The%20airwaves%20were%20filled%20with%20trailers%20for%0A%20%20%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EFinding%20Forrester%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Sean%20Connery%20absurdly%20declares%20%22you're%20the%20man%20now%2C%20dog!%22%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20Max%20Goldberg%20immediately%20recognized%20the%20power%20of%20the%20catchphrase%2C%20and%20as%20part%20of%20a%20domain-buying%20rampage%20purchased%0A%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fyourethemannowdog.com%22%3Eyourethemannowdog.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20registered%0A%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dustindiamond.com%22%3Edustindiamond.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20same%20time%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Ch3%3EYou're%20the%20man%20now%2C%20dog!%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yourethemannowdog.com%22%3EYourethemannowdog.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20created%20without%20sound%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20revisions%2C%0A%20%20%20soon%20became%20a%20legendary%20site%3A%20a%20tiled%20picture%20of%20Sean%20Connery%2C%20large%2C%20zooming%20text%20and%20a%20sound%20file%20playing%20the%20immortal%20line%20%22You're%20the%20man%20now%2C%20dog!%22%20in%20Connery's%20rolling%20Scottish%20brogue.%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Goldberg%20created%20dustindiamond.com%20with%20design%20help%20from%20Stile%2C%20from%20the%20infamous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stileproject.com%22%3EStileProject%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Ch3%3ELegal%20battles%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20In%202003%2C%20Dustin%20Diamond%2C%20who%20played%20%22Screech%22%20on%20the%20television%20show%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3ESaved%20by%20the%20Bell%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%0A%20%20%20%20sent%20a%20team%20of%20lawyers%20after%20Goldberg%2C%20trying%20to%20garner%20control%20of%20the%20dustindiamond.com%20domain.%20Goldberg%20was%20repeatedly%20threatened%2C%0A%20%20%20%20and%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20dispute%20was%20almost%20certain%20to%20end%20up%20before%20the%20courts.%20This%20period%20was%20one%20of%20unparalleled%20creativity%0A%20%20%20%20for%20Goldberg.%20It%20has%20been%20suggested%20that%20perhaps%20the%20stress%20of%20facing%20such%20an%20acclaimed%20child%20star%20in%20Internet%20court%20mobilized%0A%20%20%20%20Goldberg%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20productive%20and%20meaningful%20phases%20of%20his%20career.%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20At%20the%20same%20time%20that%20Diamond's%20lawyers%20filed%20a%20UDRP%20complaint%20against%20Goldberg%20in%20order%20to%20try%20and%20seize%20the%20domain%2C%0A%20%20%20%20Goldberg%20also%20began%20to%20find%20evidence%20that%20yourethemannowdog.com%20was%20resonating%20with%20Internet%20users%20around%20the%20globe.%0A%20%20%20%20Spoofs%20of%20the%20site%20were%20being%20created%20on%20dozens%20of%20other%20domains.%20Seeking%20to%20harness%20and%20encourage%20the%20meme%2C%0A%20%20%20%20Goldberg%20began%20to%20create%20a%20directory%20and%20mirrors%20of%20these%20spin-off%20sites.%20However%2C%20the%20site's%20popularity%20was%20such%0A%20%20%20%20that%20the%20list%20soon%20became%20too%20large%20and%20difficult%20to%20maintain%2C%20and%20Goldberg%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20site%20that%20would%20allow%0A%20%20%20%20users%20to%20easily%20create%20their%20own%20hosted%20yourethemannowdog.com%20spinoffs.%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Ch3%3EThe%20dawning%20of%20an%20era%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20On%20April%201st%2C%202004%20Goldberg%20purchased%20ytmnd.com.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20legal%20battle%20with%20Dustin%20Diamond%20was%20drawing%20to%20a%20close.%0A%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linagoldberg.com%22%20title%3D%22Lina%20Goldberg%22%3ELina%20Goldberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20YTMND%20legal%20team%2C%20had%20submitted%0A%20%20%20Goldberg's%20response%20to%20the%20UDRP%20complaint%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier%20and%20an%20answer%20was%20expected%20at%20any%20time.%20Just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20ytmnd.com%0A%20%20%20was%20purchased%2C%20the%20courts%20issued%20the%20landmark%20decision%20in%20Goldberg's%20favor%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20keep%20dustindiamond.com.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20Due%20to%20the%20precedent-setting%20nature%20of%20the%20case%2C%20Lina%20Goldberg%20lobbied%20to%20publish%20a%20press%20release%20about%20the%20groundbreaking%20decision.%0A%20%20%20Goldberg%20acquiesced%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prweb.com%2Freleases%2F2004%2F04%2Fprweb118385.htm%22%3Ethis%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%20contains%20the%20first%20mention%20of%20YTMND%20on%20the%20Internet.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EThe%20dark%20ages%20of%20YTMND%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Despite%20the%20press%20release%20being%20sent%20to%20the%20nationwide%20media%2C%20Goldberg%20had%20not%20yet%20actually%20finished%20YTMND.%0A%20%20He%20spent%20six%20days%20feverishly%20coding%20and%20designing%20the%20site%2C%20and%20on%20the%20seventh%20day%2C%20he%20rested.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20In%20early%20April%20of%202004%20Goldberg%20soft%20launched%20YTMND%20to%20a%20small%20group%20of%20friends%20and%20family.%20The%20site%20was%20riddled%20with%20bugs%2C%0A%20%20%20and%20the%20hosting%20was%20erratic%20at%20best.%20Within%20two%20weeks%20of%20the%20initial%20launch%2C%20the%20first%20YTMND%20star%20was%20born%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fpicard.ytmnd.com%22%3Epicard.ytmnd.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%20%20%20Its%20popularity%20only%20exacerbated%20the%20bandwidth%20issues%20that%20were%20causing%20instability%20and%20downtime.%20During%20this%20period%20it%20was%20not%20uncommon%20for%20YTMNDs%20to%20%22go%20dark.%22%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Late%20in%202004%20Goldberg%20took%20YTMND%20down%20due%20to%20an%20inability%20to%20cover%20the%20expense%20of%20hosting%20such%20a%20media-rich%20site.%0A%20%20In%20April%2C%202005%2C%20when%20most%20of%20the%20site%20users%20and%20even%20Goldberg%20himself%20believed%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20that%20could%20be%20done%20to%20resurrect%20the%0A%20%20site%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Freflected.net%2F%22%3EReflected.net%3C%2Fa%3E--%20longtime%20fans%20of%20YTMND--approached%20Goldberg%0A%20%20with%20a%20offer%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20hosting%20until%20he%20was%20able%20to%20host%20the%20site%20himself.%20The%20rest%20is%20history.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Ch3%3E%22The%20site%20that%20spawned%201%2C000%20memes%22%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Six%20years%20after%20YTMND%20was%20first%20created%20there%20have%20been%20over%20950%2C000%20YTMNDs%20made%20and%20over%20320%2C000%20users%20have%20registered.%20YTMND%20now%20generates%20enough%20income%20to%20cover%0A%20%20its%20massive%20hosting%20costs%20and%20new%20servers%20are%20paid%20for%20through%20site%20sponsorships%20and%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Goldberg%20has%20used%20YTMND's%20popularity%20to%20explore%20and%20promote%20issues%20relating%20to%20free%20speech.%20He%20and%20the%20YTMND%20community%20have%0A%20%20successfully%20engaged%20in%20numerous%20skirmishes%20with%20organizations%20such%20as%20the%20Church%20of%20Scientology%2C%20Gary%20Larson's%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EThe%20Far%20Side%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%0A%20%20Sega%2C%20Scholastic%20and%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EHarry%20Potter%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Pez.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20YTMND%20has%20been%20featured%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EAttack%20of%20the%20Show%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EWIRED%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3Ethe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22italic%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20YTMND%20sites%20range%20from%20the%20political%20to%20the%20nonsensical.%20Using%20sound%2C%20image%20and%20text%2C%20users%20of%20the%20site%20display%20an%20unending%20reserve%20of%20creativity%20and%20occasionally%2C%20humor.%0A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%20id%3D%22debug_box%22%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C!--%20END%20MAIN%20--%3E%0A%3Cdiv%20id%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22about%22%20href%3D%22%2Finfo%2Fabout%22%20title%3D%22about%20ytmnd%22%3Eabout%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22contact_us%22%20href%3D%22%2Finfo%2Fcontact%22%20title%3D%22contact%20us%22%3Econtact%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22page_removal%22%20href%3D%22%2Finfo%2Fremoval%22%20title%3D%22page%20removal%22%3Epage%20removal%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22advertise_here%22%20href%3D%22%2Finfo%2Fadvertising%22%20title%3D%22advertising%22%3Eadvertising%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22staff%22%20href%3D%22%2Finfo%2Fstaff%22%20title%3D%22about%20the%20staff%22%3Estaff%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20id%3D%22report_a_bug%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fbugs.ytmnd.net%2Fprojects%2Fytmnd%22%20title%3D%22report%20bugs%20and%20make%20feature%2